ning\\n\",\n=== check controller-design for PR/token creds ===\n20:  ├── Pull() — no-op (git-rest handles pulls internally)\n64:Every escalation path writes `assignee: \"\"` so the task surfaces in operator inbox.\n66:(for `human_review` paths) or `result.clearAssignee` (for cap paths) in\n87:and prompt 075 for the same reorder pattern applied to `applyTriggerCap` on\n151:| Read file | `GET /api/v1/files/{relPath}` | N/A |\n152:| Write file | `POST /api/v1/files/{relPath}` | git-rest (auto-commit) |\n153:| Delete file | `DELETE /api/v1/files/{relPath}` | git-rest (auto-commit) |\n154:| List files | `GET /api/v1/files/?glob={pattern}` | N/A |","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"call_function_xkxpeuzg3f94_1","session_id":"538dadd3-1411-457f-8798-0759f57847fd","uuid":"7a71d236-715a-43fa-baee-a1291c49ee3f","timestamp":"2026-07-01T12:15:26.653Z","subagent_type":"dark-factory:prompt-creator","task_description":"Generate prompts from spec"}
